<div class="max-w-md mx-auto p-6 bg-white shadow-md rounded-md">
  <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-center">Sign Up</h1>
  <form action="/sign_up_form" method="post" class="space-y-4">
    <div>
      <label for="phone" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">Mobile Number</label>
      <input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone" required class="mt-1 block w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md shadow-sm focus:ring-indigo-500 focus:border-indigo-500 sm:text-sm">
    </div>
    <div class="flex items-center ">
      <input type="checkbox" id="sms_consent" name="sms_consent" class="mt-2 h-4 w-4 text-indigo-600 border-gray-300 rounded focus:ring-indigo-500">
      <label for="sms_consent" class="ml-2 text-sm text-gray-600 p-2">
        By checking this box, I authorize Remind to send Customer Care SMS messages to my mobile number for alerting me of events that will take place related to school purposes. Mobile opt-in data will not be shared with third parties for promotional and marketing purposes. Message frequency varies, and data rates may apply. Replying to our messages with STOP will opt you out of receiving SMS messaging from us. Text HELP for support with SMS messaging. View <a href="/terms_of_service" class="text-indigo-600 underline">Terms and Conditions</a> <a href="/privacy_policy" class="text-indigo-600 underline">Privacy Policy</a>.
      </label>
    </div>
    <div>
      <button type="submit" class="w-full bg-indigo-600 text-black py-2 px-4 rounded-md shadow-sm hover:bg-indigo-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 focus:ring-offset-2">
        Sign Up
      </button>
    </div>
  </form>
</div>